**Improvement Triggers:**
- New patterns in 3+ files
- Repeated implementations
- Common error patterns
- New tools/libraries

**Add Rules When:**
- Common bugs preventable by rule
- Code reviews mention same feedback repeatedly
- New security/performance patterns emerge

**Quality Checks:**
- Rules must be actionable and specific
- Examples from actual code
- Up-to-date references
- Consistent enforcement